<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10268</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25847</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>国王和王后把这个消息告诉了艾伦：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25847</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33602</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个男人，一个勇敢的英雄，愿意为她而死！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33602</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40444</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>艾伦高兴得从床上跳了下来：“快带我去湖边！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40444</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45879</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>仆人们把艾伦抱到湖底的中心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45879</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49569</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一只小船停在淤泥里，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49569</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53226</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>里面装满了食物和其他东西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53226</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60251</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>王子向艾伦挥手：“我在这儿！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60251</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65069</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在咒语的作用下，艾伦只是眨了眨眼睛，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65069</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77662</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我好像认识他。”艾伦心想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77662</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80364</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>王子爬进洞里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80364</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82544</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>神奇的事情发生了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82544</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86833</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>石头里开始有水流了出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86833</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89464</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“起作用了！”王子心想，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89464</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>94032</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“湖水要重新回来了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>94032</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100680</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>艾伦让其他人离开，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100680</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105646</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后她躺下来，闭上眼睛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105646</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110473</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有你在真好！”艾伦对王子说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110473</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114235</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“和你在一起，我也很开心。”王子说道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114235</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121890</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那时候的我们总是大声地笑着。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121890</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124104</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>时间一点点过去，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124104</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129500</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>石头上的水流慢慢起了波浪。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129500</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133835</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>随着湖水的上涨，小船浮了起来，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133835</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138462</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>而公主已经睡着了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138462</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141166</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“艾伦！”王子很难过，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141166</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>144337</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你的爸爸答应过我，你会安慰我的！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>144337</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150659</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>艾伦打了个哈欠：“我太困了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150659</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156090</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>王子叹了口气：“那你睡吧，亲爱的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156090</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158456</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不用担心我。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158456</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162549</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有你在真好！”艾伦说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162549</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168280</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢你！不过我要继续睡觉了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168280</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>174090</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你能先给我一点食物吗？”王子问道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>174090</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175859</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>艾伦拿到食物，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175860</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>183411</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后第一次仔细地看了看王子的脸：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>183411</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187806</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你看起来不太好。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187807</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190498</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我很好，”王子说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190498</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193298</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我只是需要吃一点东西。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193298</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196538</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>公主给王子喂了一些食物。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196538</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198968</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不久，太阳下山了，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198968</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204207</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>月亮从湖面上升了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204207</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209370</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这时，水已经涨到了王子的腰部。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209370</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212696</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在有很多水了，”艾伦说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212696</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215816</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们去游泳吧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215816</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218896</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>王子摇了摇头，悲伤地说：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218896</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>222829</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“恐怕我再也没办法游泳了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>222829</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>230799</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>艾伦笑了：“我真傻，我忘了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>230799</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>235440</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>湖水不断上涨，一直涨到了王子的脖子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>235440</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240562</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>王子觉得很累，他知道他快要死了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240562</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244803</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我亲爱的公主，你可以吻我一下吗？”王子问道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>244803</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>248489</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这样我就能幸福地死去了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>248489</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>255999</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“当然！”艾伦俯身慢慢靠近王子的脸。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>255999</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>265690</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然！她想起来了：这是她的王子！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>265690</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>271809</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是王子快要死了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>